description: Protesters from Generation Identity held racist signs and lit flares outside Sira Sylla's office.
title: Sira Sylla: French President tweets support for targeted black MP
title_page: Sira Sylla: French President tweets support for targeted black MP - BBC News
maintext: In her tweet, Ms Sylla wrote: "I am very proud of the work that I have carried out with conviction as a French MP for three years, particularly for my constituency and African-French relations. I am more determined than ever!"
